name: First Name Terms (Ltd Edition Book)
description:
First Name Terms started life as a series of illustrations of some of my favourite actors, musicians and comedians. Originally i sold these as individual prints, but as i made more i decided to offer them as a series in the form of a hand made book. The book is A5 and is printed and assembled by me as well as being signed and numbered (ltd to an edition of 50).
If you’d like to see more of my work click <a href="http://www.benjavens.blogspot.com/"> here

name: Pigeons Are Shit (Ltd Edition Book)
description: Lets face it they are. In this book is a collection of scribbles and doodles taken from scraps of paper and notebooks, some of which date back as far as 1984 when i was 9. Again these books are A5 in size with die cut cover and are all printed, assembled, signed and numbered by yours truly (ltd to an edition of 50). If you’d like to see more of my work click <a href="http://www.benjavens.blogspot.com/"> here
